lead_paragraph: Iceland's joint coach Lars Lagerback dismissed suggestions on Friday that his team were just a well-oiled defensive unit, pointing out that by playing two strikers his side had more potency than some other nations.

headline.print_headline: Iceland Coach Says Two Strikers Gives His Side Extra Bite
